window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Welcome to the Meta Marshal Service.</p> <p>Jared just wants to be left alone.</p> <p>Unfortunately, the most powerful magi family in the world wants to kidnap one of his girlfriends.</p> <p>Jared will hunt down a rogue Plethoak, race across the country, expand his family, and destroy a top-secret experimental magic lab, all to save the women he loves.</p> <p>And in the end, the Medlar family's ultimate goal will shake the world to its core.</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
